      "value": "<p>Whenever an enemy successfully casts a spell or uses a magic item to cast a spell, the Blue Scribes can make an Opposed Willpower Test with the caster. If they prevail, roll 1d10 and consult the @Table[spell-syphon]{Spell Syphon Table}</p><p>When the Blue Scribes succeed in a Spell Syphon contest of wills (a roll of 3–10) on the table above, the spellcaster must roll an additional <strong>Very Hard (–30) Cool</strong> Test. If they fail, they gain the @Condition[Unconscious] Condition for [[/r 1d10]] hours and acquire 2 Corruption points.</p>"
